Package suncertify.db.dao.comparator

Interface Summary
IComparator IComparator provides method that allows to compare database fields without worrying about conversion from string to specific database field type.
 

Class Summary
ComparatorFactory ComparatorFactory is a factory class for database field type comparators.
IntegerComparator IntegerComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as integers - it simply converts given strings to integer objects and invokes Integer.compareTo(java.lang.Integer) method.
MoneyComparator MoneyComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as money - it simply converts given strings to money objects and invokes Money.compareTo(Money) method.
TextComparator TextComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as text - it simply invokes String.compareToIgnoreCase(String) method.
